DESCRIPTION:Join us on Wednesday\, July 8\, from 4-7 PM at Whispering Vine South Creek for a La Vieille Ferme tasting featuring Rouge\, White and Rosé from one of France's favorite everyday wine labels.\nTasting Fee: $10 per person (Buy a tasting bottle and your fee is refunded.)\nFeatured Tasting Wines:\n- La Vieille Ferme Rouge 2024 - Fresh southern French red with cassis\, crushed strawberry\, small berries\, soft spice and velvety tannins.\n- La Vieille Ferme White 2025 - Bright white with white peach\, jasmine\, mimosa blossom\, nectarine\, saline lift and yuzu freshness.\n- La Vieille Ferme Rosé - Powder-pink rosé with roses\, red fruit\, strawberry\, peach\, lively acidity and a mineral finish.\nSpecial Bottle Deal: La Vieille Ferme Rosé magnums will also be available for $19.99. They are the perfect size for entertaining\, BBQs and lake days.\nBuy a tasting bottle and your fee is refunded.
LOCATION:85 Foothill Rd Ste 1 Reno\, NV 89511
SUMMARY:La Vieille Ferme Tasting
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR